title: Worst Apology Video on YouTube Just Dropped...
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at the worst apology video uploaded on this platform. Colleen Ballinger was recently through some pretty serious accusations and in response she decided to turn the whole response into a song and dance, quite literally it's the wildest thing I've seen in so long. Thanks for watching!
